 istitle() rpartition() 13.6.7.1 Regex Extractor Extract capture groups in the regex pattern, by default in DataFrame (expand=True). Series.str.extract(self, pat, flags=0, expand=True) - expand=True: if result is single column, make it a Series instead of Dataframe. s = pd.Series([&#39;a1&#39;, &#39;b2&#39;, &#39;c3&#39;]) print( &#39; Extracted Dataframe:
